Linux 2.6 for 64-bit pcs (meta-package), linux-vserver support
	
this package depends on the latest linux kernel 2.6 and modules for use on
pcs with amd64 or intel 64 processors.

this kernel includes support for linux-vserver virtualization.

this kernel also runs on a xen hypervisor.  it supports only unprivileged
(domu) operation.